"""
        Test the positron lines for 'e e'.
        """
lns1_new = self.sm1.positron_lines(self.e_cm1)
lns2_new = self.sm2.positron_lines(self.e_cm2)
assert_allclose(lns1_new['e e']['bf'], self.lns1_old['e e']['bf'], rtol=0.0001)
assert_allclose(lns1_new['e e']['energy'], self.lns1_old['e e']['energy'],
    rtol=0.0001)
assert_allclose(lns2_new['e e']['bf'], self.lns2_old['e e']['bf'], rtol=0.0001)
assert_allclose(lns2_new['e e']['energy'], self.lns2_old['e e']['energy'],
    rtol=0.0001)
